    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no point in trying to fix it anymore. like, no matter how much i fight to be myself, the world just stays this way. it's like i'm just waiting for something to break. do you think it's actually possible to ever really win this? or is it just... better to stop fighting?",
